data.description: Move-in ready home in a quaint neighborhood just minutes to town and close by TTU and CRMC. Walking up you have a covered front porch and a spacious driveway with a true two car garage + ample storage/work space. Once inside you have hardwood flooring, neutral paint, an open living room right off the kitchen with ample cabinetry + dining area. Your main level also provides your master suite with a great walk-in closet and an open back deck. Upstairs you have your other two spacious bedrooms, a full bath, and a bonus room with newer flooring.  13 month home warranty for peace of mind.
